      "value": "<p>            You have learned to sanctify your armaments, coating them and the powers you wield with the nature of your connection to Senna.</p>\n<p>When you take this feat, choose an affinity that represents the connection you have with Senna: Radiance, Gloom or Spirit. All your spectral arms and focus spells gains the Sanctified trait, and gains a quality based on this connection:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Radiance</strong>: Your spectral arms and focus spells gain the Sanctified and Holy trait.</li>\n<li><strong>Gloom</strong>: Your spectral arms and focus spells gain the Sanctified and Unholy trait.</li>\n<li><strong>Spirit</strong>: Your spectral arms and focus spells have the ghost-touch property.</li>\n</ul>"
